Fenerbahce Chairman Appeals Arrest in Turkish Soccer Probe, Sabah Reports

-- B y   E m r e   P e k e r
-- 
2011-07-19T06:35:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-19/fenerbahce-chairman-appeals-arrest-in-turkish-soccer-probe-sabah-reports.html
Fenerbahce SK Chairman Aziz Yildirim
is appealing his arrest in an investigation of an alleged match-
fixing scheme, Sabah reported.  Attorneys for the imprisoned chairman of  Turkey ’s soccer
champions pointed to Yildirim’s health problems, asking an
Istanbul court to release him on bail, Sabah said, without
saying where it got the information.  Click here for web link  To contact the reporter on this story:
